ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\frac{d}{dM_r} \ln (T + \Delta T) 
= \frac{d}{dM_r} \ln \left\{ T \left( 1 + \frac{\Delta T}{T} \right) \right\} 
= \frac{d \ln T}{dM_r} + \frac{d}{dM_r} \ln \left( 1 + \frac{\Delta T}{T} \right) 
\approx  \frac{d \ln T}{dM_r} + \frac{d}{dM_r} \left(\frac{\Delta T}{T} \right)\]

